# OWL Sing Together — Website

The OWL Sing Together public website, blog, store, newsletter, admin CRM, and curriculum portal.

> **Source of truth lives in the Obsidian vault** at `../OWL-Obsidian-Brain/`. Always read [`CLAUDE.md`](./CLAUDE.md) before making changes.

## Stack

Next.js 15 · TypeScript · Tailwind CSS · App Router · `src/` directory · ESLint · Framer Motion · Sanity (CMS) · Supabase · Shopify · Stripe · Beehiiv · Resend · Cloudflare R2.

Full stack reference: [`../OWL-Obsidian-Brain/11_Tech_Requirements/TECH_STACK.md`](../OWL-Obsidian-Brain/11_Tech_Requirements/TECH_STACK.md).

## Getting started

```bash
# install dependencies
npm install

# copy env template and fill in real values
cp .env.local.example .env.local

# run dev server
npm run dev
```

Open <http://localhost:3000>.

## Scripts

- `npm run dev` — local dev server
- `npm run build` — production build
- `npm run start` — production server
- `npm run lint` — ESLint
- `npm run typecheck` — `tsc --noEmit`

## Project structure

```
src/
├── app/                    # App Router pages (one folder per route)
├── components/             # Reusable components, grouped by domain
│   └── ui/                 # Design-system primitives (Button, Card, Chip, etc.)
├── lib/
│   ├── tokens.ts           # Brand tokens (mirrors DESIGN_STYLE_GUIDE.md)
│   └── cn.ts               # Tailwind classname merger
public/                     # Static assets
```

